00:19:42.920 --> 00:19:44.280
Di mana dia menyentuhmu, Lakshmi?

00:19:44.840 --> 00:19:46.200
Di mana dia menyentuhmu?

00:19:48.480 --> 00:19:49.480
Apakah dia menyentuhmu di sini?

00:19:50.680 --> 00:19:51.920
Apakah dia menyentuhmu di sini?

00:19:52.000 --> 00:19:54.240
Apakah dia menyentuhmu di sini?  Di mana dia menyentuhmu?
- Di Sini!

00:20:12.360 --> 00:20:13.360
Di Sini.

00:20:37.840 --> 00:20:38.960
Dia menyentuhku di sini.

00:20:50.120 --> 00:20:52.520
Rishi menyentuh jiwaku, Malishka.

00:21:14.880 --> 00:21:21.440
"Ya Tuhan!"

